#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;Play as the Nightshade!^reset;

The Nightshade are a subspecies of the Floran whose heads are fruit! Variations might resemble tomatoes, onions, pumpkins...a pomegranate?

The design was chiefly inspired by the mandragora as styled in the Final Fantasy world of Ivalice.

Requires a character extender!

contains:
1 playable race
slightly modified floran sprite
~95 hair styles

Made using MRMT!

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

